thread.title: BRIEF-Greencross Posts Hy Profit From Ordinary Activities After Tax Attributable Of $23.2 Mln

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Greencross Posts Hy Profit From Ordinary Activities After Tax Attributable Of $23.2 Mln
text:
Feb 20 (Reuters) - Greencross Ltd:
* ‍INTERIM DIVIDEND PER ORDINARY SHARE 10.0 CENTS​ * HY REVENUE FROM ORDINARY ACTIVITIES $433.3 MILLION, UP 8.8 PERCENT
* ‍HY PROFIT FROM ORDINARY ACTIVITIES AFTER TAX ATTRIBUTABLE TO OWNERS UP 8.9%, $23.2 MILLION
* HY PROFIT FROM ORDINARY ACTIVITIES AFTER TAX ATTRIBUTABLE UP 8.9 PERCENT TO $23.2 MILLION ​
* “BUSINESS CONTINUES TO PERFORM IN LINE WITH PLAN IN FY2018 YTD”
* EXPECTS ITS EFFECTIVE TAX RATE FOR FULL YEAR FY2018 WILL BE ABOUT 28 PERCENT Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
